-h%E1%BB%A9ng-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-qu%E1%BA%A7n-c%C3%B4ng/poem-x2D4zVhf9YbxgypolcKI9w">Thuỷ túc khiển hứng phụng trình quần công - 水宿遣興奉呈群公</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-xu%C3%A2n/poem-BUto1rgRApFmfx6OMKzU9w">Thưởng xuân - 賞春</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1t/author-QedIvlr4BuYMTZh_TuTCTA">Nguyễn Đức Đạt</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Tranh/poem-xjO4AuM4KPCKObpGXw5nUA">Tranh - 筝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%C6%B0-V%C3%A2n-thi%C3%AAn-tr%C3%B9ng-thu%E1%BB%B7-thi%C3%AAn-tr%C3%B9ng/poem-MiyYYmc1QXAWyDEJZTRizQ">Trường tương tư (Vân thiên trùng, thuỷ thiên trùng) - 長相思（雲千重，水千重）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br></div>	</div>
